What is Sorare Football?

June 19, 2021

Sorare Football is a global fantasy football game, featuring more than 300 football clubs from around the world and more than 40 football leagues. What makes Sorare unique is that you have the opportunity to play with officially licensed digital collectible cards.

  • Collect officially licensed digital cards, featuring the world's best football players and prospects
  • Build five-player (5) lineups from the cards in your collection, including one (1) goalkeeper, one (1) defender, one (1) midfielder, one (1) forward, and one (1) extra player
  • Enter your lineups into a variety of competitions, each lasting 3-4 days
  • Scoring is based on the real-life performance of the players in your lineup
  • With every competition, your players earn more XP, making them more powerful
  • Compete with players on global leaderboards for Sorare digital player cards, ETH, and VIP experiences
  • Buy, sell, trade, and collect your cards with complete freedom
  • Visit The Sorare Marketplace to build your collection and compete with other players

In traditional digital games, you collect and use in-game items but you don't own them. Sorare's digital player cards have provable scarcity (fixed and limited supply), provenance, true ownership, and complete freedom of movement, thanks to blockchain technology. Your Sorare cards are truly yours. With an officially licensed digital collectible card from Sorare, you can use it in Sorare competitions, keep it as a collectible, transfer it to another platform, sell it, trade it, play it in another game, create your own game where you can use it, etc.

Build your collection and compete with other players.
